features: OSHA COMPLIANCE: Meet the latest standards with this MFASCO first aid cabinet, designed to fulfill the ANSI/OSHA 2021 requirements for Class B First Aid Kits. Ideal for creating a safer work environment, this first aid kit is a must-have for any office, shop, or commercial setting.

VERSATILE PLACEMENT: Make safety a priority in your business or workspace. This first aid kit box can be conveniently wall-mounted for easy access or carried around, ensuring immediate assistance in times of need.

EFFORTLESS RESTOCKING: The MFASCO commercial first aid kit comes with an easy restock card. Never worry about running out of necessary supplies - the restock card makes inventory management a breeze for your business.

VISIBILITY AND ACCESSIBILITY: This large first aid kit features an attractive first aid label, ensuring it stands out in any environment. The supplies inside the robust metal cabinet are easily accessible, ensuring quick response during emergencies.

INCLUSIVE FIRST AID SOLUTIONS: The MFASCO wall mount first aid kit offers comprehensive aid solutions for a variety of situations. It includes adhesive bandages, antiseptic wipes, gauze pads, a CPR mask, and more. This complete kit is suitable for any home or business, and it's designed for efficient first aid application. Ideal for businesses looking for OSHA compliant first aid kits, or as a comprehensive home first aid kit for complete family care.

reviews.reviewText: Comes ready to go!! Love that it has a refill barcode to scan on the side!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You get what you pay for.. very nice!
reviews.reviewText: Solid metal case with Handel.Just like the one at work, has all the finger tip and knuckle bandages with all the other little stuff. Instant ice pack, emergency blanket, tweezers. etc I like the little extra space for my own personal stuff like aspirin or my liquid bandage. Few extra pockets on door too..But for most part, it's packed! The bonus is the restock number right on side of box with qr code also so restocking should be easy..Hangs nicely, I installed cup holders on side for my hydrogen peroxide and alcohol bottle since that's the real first aid. Lol
